name: VORTEX SKYTRIANGLE #01
description: Artist: Betty Mü, Video Loop, 724x720 Pixels, 01:00 Minutes, Original Creation Date: 12. February 2021, By showing cyclical forms that are constantly changing, Betty Mü’s surreal videomapping installation draws the viewer’s gaze into the vortex of a hypnotic time warp. A vast current of stimuli forces the viewer into a dialogue in order to decipher the story that is circling around. The VORTEX series started 2016.
